rComments: He is very knowledgeable on the subject but is hard to follow in class. I found it difficult to take notes because he often gets off track and loses his train of thought, or doesn't finish his ideas completely. I find his course delivery much too convoluted for an intro course. As well, his midterm was poorly designed and the final was worth 50%
